OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 24 May to Tue 2 Jun
OL,6,FWarm and dry for most on Sunday and
OL,7,FBank Holiday Monday. Through the
OL,8,Ffollowing week, high pressure is
OL,9,Fexpected to remain in place for much
OL,10,Fof the UK, meaning fine weather likely
OL,11,Fto continue for most places. Some
OL,12,Fpatchy rain may affect the far north
OL,13,Fat times and perhaps a few showers in
OL,14,Fthe far south. Temperatures are
OL,15,Fexpected to be above normal, feeling
OL,16,Fvery warm at times with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
